resources.string: Note: it Does not store the number
This Application uses WhatsApp services to start a conversation with any number included.

This Cleaner does not clear cache or something absurd to boost your WhatsApp, it goes deep inside and delete junk to make your WhatsApp smooth. NOTE: This process will delete all the Sent folders from your WhatsApp media but you are not going to lose any data during this process.
